---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
import Button from "../components/UI/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Find a Partner Clinic | BEMA - Healthcare Access for Florida's Working Families"
  description="Find a BEMA partner clinic in Florida offering Direct Primary Care, Eye Care, and Mental Health services coordinated through your BEMA membership."
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Find a Partner Clinic"
    subtitle="BEMA partner clinics serve members directly across Florida, delivering Direct Primary Care, Eye Care, and Mental Health services while BEMA handles the coordination in between."
    imageSrc="/images/providers-clinic-network.jpg"
    imageAlt="A welcoming independent clinic entrance in a Florida neighborhood setting, professional and community focused."
  />

  <section class="section-pad bg-bema-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mb-10 max-w-3xl">
        <h2>Our Partner Clinic Network</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-bema-khaki/40 bg-bema-khaki-light/35 p-8 text-center">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="mx-auto mb-5 h-12 w-12 text-bema-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 21s7-5.2 7-12a7 7 0 10-14 0c0 6.8 7 12 7 12z"></path>
          <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"></circle>
        </svg>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-bema-green">Our partner clinic network is growing. Clinics will be listed here by name, location, and service type as the network launches in your area.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-bema-green/80">Clinics will be listed here with name, location, service types, and contact information.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad bg-bema-khaki-light/20">
    <div class="container grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Clinic partners</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3">Partner clinics that want to do more for their community.</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-bema-green/85">BEMA is built around independent clinics that are already delivering excellent care and want a coordination partner that handles everything outside the exam room. When a clinic joins the BEMA network it gains access to a steady membership population without taking on the administrative weight that usually comes with it. No insurance billing. No claims processing. No coordination overhead. BEMA absorbs all of it. Partner clinics in the BEMA network serve two populations through the same practice. BEMA members access care through their monthly program service fee. The charitable mission population is funded entirely through donations with zero operational dollars redirected to cover it. The clinic focuses on the patient in front of them. BEMA handles everything else before and after that appointment.</p>
        <div class="mt-8 border-l-4 border-bema-khaki bg-bema-white p-6 font-medium text-bema-green">
          BEMA absorbs the coordination friction so that partner clinics can focus entirely on clinical work.
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <Button href="/contact">Contact Us About Partnering</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/providers-clinic-network.jpg"
        alt="An independent clinic setting with a warm and professional feel, a small practice focused entirely on patient care."
        class="min-h-80 w-full rounded-lg border border-bema-khaki/40 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
